Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew it would turn out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have taken the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't like it from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's just a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, no hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I said a doctor, but not a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hellblau Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to a hospital, the police will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll be back in prison again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to get to that\Nunderground doctor's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Hellblau Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- if you're alive, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Hurry the hell up!{\i}\N- if you're alive, you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Hurry the hell up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hellblau Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing good ever comes from\Ngetting involved with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,get to Dr. Tenma quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.33,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}Two Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The person you're about to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:12.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,500)\pos(360,340)}I Hate This Job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is someone you wouldn't be able\Nto see under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should've brought my autograph book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This man, Martin, is my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to speak with him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll really kill you if you screw something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been with The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost three years, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You got out rather quickly, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an exemplary inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're exemplary when it\Ncomes to doing jobs, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Any job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Except?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too thrilled with jobs that involve women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't be picky about my jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to get involved with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This job does involve a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to look after a certain woman for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An unpleasant job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to pick up a certain woman from DÃ¼sseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you say you don't like to get involved with women...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be perfect for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to keep things professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Eva Heinemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think my name matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to take you to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Told by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A man wearing glasses and an expensive suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A man wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not with Roberto's group, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he seems to be a very important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to go, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too thrilled about this, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be my bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's part of my job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than getting killed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unpleasant bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she shakes her ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of her perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk about something if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really feel like talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Any drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you're traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm traveling alone myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if you don't mind, could you please\Ntell me where you'll be staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here. This is my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman asked me for a drink, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lay a finger on this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk while you're eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I'll talk if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you drink alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom was a terrible alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mind if you drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother probably had a reason why she had to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason I have to drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if you don't like eating without a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to have a fiancÃ©.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a Japanese surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with brilliant skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I tried to kill my former fiancÃ©.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to kill that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story is better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I... actually pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend was on top of some guy in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot the guy along with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,until the gun ran out of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The room was filled with the smell of\Nher blood, the smell of his blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the smell of her perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was standing alone in the middle of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unpleasant job...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My employer is waiting at this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you're dressed isn't suited for this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's room 1014.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the man with the glasses will say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that woman refuses his deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this unpleasant job will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have to deal with that woman anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He said I could use this card as much as I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hate this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This place next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But they sell men's suits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to look decent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have a man in my company looking so shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Necktie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You look a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,wear your tie properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop walking around with your shoulders\Nslouched like a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was walking normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "normal" isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you have to guard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure I won't be embarrassed.\Nno matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put your elbow on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fork in your left hand, knife in your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make any noises when you're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were the daughter of\Nthe director of a big hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought it was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I brought you to this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you just seemed like an alcoholic woman,\Nno matter how I looked at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite different now, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a classy lady, no two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann just returned to where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the Job that was given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To attend several parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a fun job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be my escort, a gentleman worthy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting more unpleasant by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to finally be back on home ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are all these people talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell what language they're speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't at this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My job here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wasn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care where!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and take me away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know why this woman's hand was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've managed to somehow survive the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you return to the place where you belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My life used to be like that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I returned to that world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the real me would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,places like this bar are the only places\Nwhere you feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't belong in a place like this, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not places like that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place for me, no matter where I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that after I've finished this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll surely be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be better than staying a mess and\Ngetting killed by Roberto in DÃ¼sseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be better to die as the\Nwell-dressed Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's all the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,once I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad habit came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I suddenly thought to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wanted to protect this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's why I'm going to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,everything to Dr. Tenma right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have had to go to a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,see something so terrifying.
